headline: Food distributor Sysco cuts annual forecasts on weak restaurant traffic
summary: The company added that the wildfires in California and bad weather conditions also weighed on demand for supply of fresh fruits, vegetables and meat products to restaurants.  Sysco's customers include restaurant chains KFC, Subway, Burger King and Applebees.
